{"tid":1652231,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人無力感十足...？好想回到以前..","createTime":"2019-10-13T15:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T17:34:09.000Z","uid":106706,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"edea5ff50dccdf16be3e3c4438934b1682b6e6a6","tid":1652231,"uid":106706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"不管香港環境..感情...工作都係無力感十足，我都唔知自己可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好辛苦...<br />\n首先香港環境唔洗講，好想出份力..但感覺好似改變唔到...我都唔知可以做咩去改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己身體唔好，又驚連累埋人..加上冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個人可以做咩？<br />\n<br />\n在感情方面，我根本失敗，同以前ex散佐大半年，依家同個新既開始...因為佢話唔介意我諗ex 都肯同我開始，但我發現好似試下都覺得唔啱咁....唔知點解好似欠d嘢...同佢一齊冇耐，感覺佢好似唔係我那個mr right 但可能我問題...未放下以前...而佢又不斷表白，我朋友又俾壓力我 話唔一齊但成日好奇怪，所以我先一齊..我嘗試投入感情...係開心既...但我好似將佢同ex不斷比較...我好似未諗通咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在工作方面，剛剛轉新工，冇咩滿足感...之前失業大半年...終於有工...但我感覺自己為錢而做，好累...<br />\n<br />\n在自己健康方面，多病...冇人理....ex都係因為對我不理我而散...感覺自己根本就係個負累<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我...可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178f74407d7299bf965fb78d0d04dd4f0f3e3a65","tid":1652231,"uid":106706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:21:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"306adbf7ee95366f7e9492af3475dd77d756dd07","tid":1652231,"uid":106706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"d56107521e78b22c1ccd110985739d861788c2c4","tid":1652231,"uid":106706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:21:31